title: 144. Personal Responsibility Ft. Jason Khalipa
itunes:title: 144. Personal Responsibility Ft. Jason Khalipa
description: We need more healthy discussions amongst people with dissimilar opinions. On today’s episode, Andy and the crew are joined by former CrossFit Games Athlete turned entrepreneur Jason Khalipa. They discuss contrasting views regarding the vaccine mandates, 75 Hard and the media misreporting the facts and why personal responsibility and selfless leadership is the need of the hour for America to get back to its real glory.
